        <briefdescription>
<para>Dot product of Q7 vectors. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Scaling and Overflow Behavior</title><para>The intermediate multiplications are in 1.7 x 1.7 = 2.14 format and these results are added to an accumulator in 18.14 format. Nonsaturating additions are used and there is no danger of wrap around as long as the vectors are less than 2^18 elements long. The return result is in 18.14 format.</para>
</simplesect>
